heading: Feature display order
sortMostRecent: Sort features with recent dates on top
sortLeastRecent: Sort features with older dates on top
mostToLeast: Sort features with larger values on top
leastToMost: Sort features with smaller values on top
smallToLarge: Sort features with smaller values on top
largeToSmall: Sort features with larger values on top
orderByTooltip: Choose a field to determine the display order of features on the map.
